# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# SPA fallback for notebook detail pages: a 200 (soft rewrite) serves the
# notebook SPA HTML while preserving the requested URL so client-side
# routing can read the notebook id from the path. The Pages _worker.js no
# longer special-cases /notebook/*; this rule handles it at the assets layer.
#
# NOTE: destination is the bare "/notebook" pretty URL, NOT "/notebook.html".
# Pages "Pretty URLs" intercept "GET /notebook.html" and 308-redirect it to
# "/notebook"; a 200 rewrite targeting /notebook.html therefore surfaces a
# 308 to the client instead of the HTML. Targeting "/notebook" serves
# notebook.html directly (pretty URL -> notebook.html) with no redirect leak.
/notebook/*  /notebook  200